		</summary>
		<param name="changeType">One of the <see cref="System.IO.WatcherChangeTypes"/> values, which represents the kind of change detected in the file system.</param>
		<param name="directory">The root directory of the affected file or directory.</param>
		<param name="name">The name of the affected file or directory.</param>
		<seealso cref="System.IO.FileSystemWatcher"/>
		<seealso cref="System.IO.WatcherChangeTypes"/>
	</doc><doc for="FileSystemEventArgs.FullPath">
		<summary>
